Package gov.sandia.gmp.util.numerical.matrix

Class LSQRDD.PartialResult

java.lang.Object
gov.sandia.gmp.util.numerical.matrix.LSQRDD.PartialResult
Enclosing class:
LSQRDD
public class LSQRDD.PartialResult extends Object
A dummy CompletionService result class returned to the caller after each task is finished. The result contains the row/column start/stop values for each task.
